  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA9">
<l>aruḷē yulakelā māḷvippa tīca</l>
<l>ṉaruḷē piṟappaṟuppa tāṉā - laruḷālē</l>
<l>meypporuḷai nōkkum vitiyuṭaiyē ṉeññāṉṟu</l>
<l>mepporuḷu māva teṉakku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Grace alone rules the whole world. The lord’s</l>
<l>grace alone cuts off birth. Therefore, by grace alone</l>
<l>I possess a guideline towards true meaning. Always</l>
<l>every object/meaning is mine.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
